<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10727767>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Pterodacna boucheti gen. et sp. nov. A. Holotype, side view, basal length 1.9 mm (MNHN- IM-2013-67323). B. Dorsal view, length 1.7 mm (paratype, MNHN-IM-2000-38245). C. Sculptural detail of holotype, scale bar =100 μm. D. Protoconch of holotype, scale bar = 100 μm. E. Pitted microsculpture of protoconch, scale bar =25 μm (paratype, MNHN-IM-2000-38245). F. Ventral view of preserved specimen, scale bar =250 μm (paratype, MNHN-IM-2000-38245)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10727767/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10727769>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Pterodacna boucheti gen. et sp. nov., radula (paratype, MNHN-IM-2000-38245). A. Entire width of radula, anterior third, scale bar = 25 μm. B. Entire width of radula, posterior third, laterals 2–4 folded behind lateral 1, scale bar= 25 μm. C. Detail of rachidian, lateral and inner marginal teeth, scale bar =10 μm. D. Details of marginal teeth, scale bar =10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10727769/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

